Sælir Vaktarar
Hér hef ég Coolermaster Hyper 412S örgjörva kælingu tilsölu
Keypt ný í tölvulistanum 2 Nóvember 2012
Allt fylgir
Kostar ný 8.990kr
CPU Socket	Intel Socket:
LGA 2011 / 1366 / 1156 / 1155 / 775 *
AMD Socket:
FM1 / AM3+ / AM3 / AM2+ / AM2
The Hyper 412S CPU Cooler is designed for optimum heat dissipation at low fan speeds. 
This is thanks to wider fin gaps and a precise heat pipe layout that directs each of their four 
heat pipes across CPU "hot zones". These heat pipes are arranged using Cooler Masters
patented CDC(tm) technology, creating a virtual vapor chamber for maximum cooling 
potential. The 412S comes equipped with an ultra low speed silent mode fan adapter to 
virtually erase noise levels.
